2.【Multiple Functions and Widely Used】- This LED wall clock has has multiple functions, it can as timer, alarm clock, clock, press mode button or use the Remote Control to change mode, very easy to operate, have Snooze, 12/24H, DST, temperature display in ℃ or ℉, this electric clock is very suitable for Gym/ Shop/ Living room/ Mall/ Warehouse/ Garage/ Office/ MeetingRoom/ Classroom/ Library/ Hospital/ Church/ Nursing Home.

3.【Count Up/Down Timer and Easy to Hang】- This rectangle wall clock max timing period for 29 hr 59 min 59 sec, good helper for time management, fitness, exam review and competition timing! The large wall clocks for living room décor comes with a paper ruler card and a hanging backboard to make hanging more easier! This office clock have a fold-out back frame, so you can placed it on the desktop or bookshelf too.

4.【Outlet Powered with Memorized Backup Battery】- Our digital clock for wall is outlet powered, not need to worry about battery running out of power or replacing batteries regularly, 2 AAA memory batteries is included to ensure the time system continues to operate when power outage and preserves settings , screen is off in this condition. So not need to recalibration/reset time when outlet power is restoration supply!

5.【Reassured After Sales Service】- Our garage clock have passed US 21 Security projects testing, if this gym clock breaks or damaged in shipping, or you change your mind, please feel free to contact us(how to: click on your order--contact seller), you can choose to replace it or only refund not need to return in 24 hours!

6.【3 Modes for Hourly Chime】- This wall clock can chime when it reaches the full hour and the chime will last for less than 50 seconds based on the ringtone you choose, and you can adjusting the volume of the chime through the remote control! Press"Alarm Set" for 2 seconds and then press "+" or "-" to select the chime ringtone, and then press"SET" to choose the ringing mode, MOD 1 (default mode) : Not chime, MOD 2: Hourly chime, MOD 3: Chime from 6:00 to 21:00, and 22:00 to 5:00 Not chime.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It's just so cool!
reviews.reviewText: Maybe I'm easily impressed, but I think this thing is awesome! There's not that much to it- it's a giant digital clock/timer. The timer and stopwatch functions are serviceable. The remote is bigger than I expected, but still pocket sized, and it has great functionality. The display itself is impressively bright. The automatic brightness sensor is cool, but I doubt I'll use it. The alarm sounds are also higher quality than I expected. Overall, it has one job, and it does it well!

reviews.reviewText: We bought this for our new shop - it’s perfect size and the lettering for the time temp date and day of the week shows up so well. Love the red!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars BIG, bright clock!!!
reviews.reviewText: VERY large, clear display with brightness adjustment. Timer and alarm functions are nice touches, are the surprisingly high-quality chime options. Remote is reasonably useful.I would have liked to see atomic timekeeping at this price point, in addition to a customizable chime schedule. The manual instructions are somewhat misleading in places, but the corrections are easy enough to figure out.A good value overall.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent Digital Clock
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for a digital clock for our office. I was quoted over $400 by another vendor for a similar clock. I am pleased that I went with this clock, large numbers, easy to read from a distance. I would have liked to have the option of different colors of display lighting. But very please with this purchase.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This Clock is a Must Have!
reviews.reviewText: This led wall clock is pleasantly bigger than I expected! It has a ton of settings and a remote. The alarm sounds cool kinda like a church bell and we love it. We put it in our garage with our gym equipment! It has a timer and a stopwatch which is really useful during workouts. Definitely worth the price and great quality!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I got the clock and put it up right away. It was bright, and easy to read. I loved it. Last night the clock was fine but when I looked at it this morning the dark face had fallen off and was lying on the floor. I know there are occasional problems with manufactured items so I contacted the seller and they immediately took very good care of me and I am happy to have such an awesome clock!! Excellent customer service. I will buy another one for my garage soon.
